WEBVTT

01:32.240 --> 01:34.990
[How dare you!?]

01:36.039 --> 01:40.020
[Episode 25]

01:45.460 --> 01:46.259
Your Majesty.

01:47.000 --> 01:47.800
Your Majesty.

01:48.070 --> 01:48.870
The antidote.

01:50.310 --> 01:51.229
The antidote!

01:53.280 --> 01:55.009
-Your Majesty.
-Your Majesty.

01:55.789 --> 01:56.990
Give me the antidote!

01:57.590 --> 01:58.850
Where is the antidote?

01:58.920 --> 01:59.850
Give it to me now.

02:00.280 --> 02:01.010
Give it to me!

02:01.950 --> 02:02.400
Hurry, give it to me!

02:02.400 --> 02:04.560
Don't you want
your little Crown Prince to live?

02:04.560 --> 02:06.790
-Give me the antidote!
-If anything happens to her,

02:06.790 --> 02:08.780
all of you will die!

02:09.030 --> 02:09.590
-Your Majesty.
-Your Majesty.

02:09.590 --> 02:11.190
Your Majesty, please don't.

02:13.310 --> 02:14.840
You Xia people

02:16.310 --> 02:18.870
will die a terrible death!

02:29.720 --> 02:30.980
Where's the antidote?

02:34.890 --> 02:36.690
-Give me the antidote!
-CEO Dan!

02:36.900 --> 02:37.410
CEO Dan.

02:37.870 --> 02:38.329
Stop it.

02:38.910 --> 02:39.510
Let go now.

02:40.520 --> 02:40.980
CEO Dan.

02:42.800 --> 02:43.230
Dan...

02:44.120 --> 02:46.720
We haven't eaten the hot pot
in the chamber yet.

02:47.680 --> 02:49.680
Mr. Bei made a hot and sour soup base.

02:53.040 --> 02:54.170
And we still have...

02:55.930 --> 02:57.890
so many things we haven't done yet.

03:00.750 --> 03:01.520
Remember?

03:03.540 --> 03:04.320
Look at me.

03:04.750 --> 03:05.590
Look at me.

03:16.160 --> 03:17.440
I'm going

03:19.590 --> 03:21.680
home...

03:24.680 --> 03:27.840
I'm going home...

03:41.770 --> 03:42.630
It's all right.

03:45.630 --> 03:46.490
It's all right.

03:48.900 --> 03:49.490
Wanyin.

03:51.360 --> 03:51.980
Yes.

03:59.950 --> 04:00.750
Your Majesty!

04:04.360 --> 04:04.930
Eunuch An.

04:04.930 --> 04:05.550
Yes.

04:06.590 --> 04:07.370
Stay here.

04:08.750 --> 04:09.680
Without my word,

04:10.750 --> 04:12.750
the Empress Dowager has to stay alive.

04:12.750 --> 04:13.190
Yes.

04:13.940 --> 04:15.000
Imperial Physician Xiao.

04:15.000 --> 04:15.440
Yes.

04:15.740 --> 04:17.720
Take the little Crown Prince
back to the palace.

04:17.720 --> 04:18.779
Guard him closely.

04:19.010 --> 04:20.410
No one is to approach him!

04:20.430 --> 04:20.750
Yes.

04:21.399 --> 04:21.930
Guards!

04:23.040 --> 04:25.040
His Majesty has fainted from grief.

04:25.160 --> 04:27.160
Take him back to the palace quickly!

04:36.490 --> 04:37.050
Your Highness.

04:37.050 --> 04:37.860
How is it?

04:38.600 --> 04:39.720
Is the Empress Dowager dead?

04:39.720 --> 04:41.370
There's a skilled young physician

04:41.370 --> 04:43.570
who's helping to keep her barely alive.

04:44.070 --> 04:45.540
What about the Emperor?

04:45.630 --> 04:46.890
The palace is in chaos.

04:47.680 --> 04:48.580
They say

04:49.270 --> 04:51.800
the Emperor collapsed
from excessive grief.

04:51.950 --> 04:55.080
Even the little Crown Prince
fainted and was taken away.

04:58.190 --> 05:00.680
I knew that old thing

05:01.780 --> 05:03.890
wouldn't die so easily.

05:05.600 --> 05:06.880
Perhaps this time

05:08.360 --> 05:10.420
we won't even need to act ourselves,

05:11.750 --> 05:15.050
and they'll fight
until both sides are destroyed.

05:18.190 --> 05:18.720
Wanyin.

05:20.310 --> 05:21.240
Are you alright?

05:21.270 --> 05:22.600
Imperial Physician Xiao sent me a message

05:22.600 --> 05:23.680
and told me what happened.

05:23.680 --> 05:24.720
I was terrified!

05:24.950 --> 05:25.680
Are you okay?

05:26.240 --> 05:26.800
I'm fine.

05:28.240 --> 05:28.970
It's CEO Dan.

05:30.600 --> 05:31.730
He's not doing well.

05:36.800 --> 05:38.240
I temporarily used acupressure

05:38.240 --> 05:40.120
to stop the poison from spreading.

05:40.120 --> 05:42.380
But this poison is extremely dangerous.

05:42.630 --> 05:45.120
It will make him delirious
when it takes effect.

05:45.120 --> 05:45.590
Wanyin,

05:46.000 --> 05:47.330
please watch him for me.

05:47.430 --> 05:49.630
I need to test this poison powder again.

05:57.240 --> 05:58.240
It's all my fault.

05:58.950 --> 06:01.070
I knew the Empress Dowager
wasn't a good person,

06:01.070 --> 06:02.600
yet I still wasn't on guard.

06:03.750 --> 06:06.080
I saw the Crown Prince
as soon as I entered,

06:06.240 --> 06:07.840
but it never crossed my mind.

06:09.430 --> 06:10.690
Don't blame yourself.

06:11.000 --> 06:13.170
Who would be wary of a young kid?

06:13.430 --> 06:14.260
Besides,

06:14.680 --> 06:16.230
you reacted fast enough.

06:16.510 --> 06:17.620
Most of the poison

06:17.830 --> 06:19.180
was blocked by you.

06:19.480 --> 06:20.390
That's true.

06:21.800 --> 06:23.800
But how come nothing happened to me?

06:23.930 --> 06:25.330
CEO Dan only touched a bit

06:26.040 --> 06:27.840
and suddenly became delirious.

06:30.390 --> 06:31.890
I feel something's off,

06:32.560 --> 06:34.020
but I can't figure out why.

06:35.480 --> 06:37.210
The poison knows who to poison.

06:38.360 --> 06:39.290
What do you mean?

06:39.920 --> 06:41.090
I'm just guessing.

06:41.950 --> 06:45.350
It's the same poison,
but it only works on specific people...

06:45.870 --> 06:47.190
The Crown Prince

06:49.159 --> 06:51.490
must've sprinkled poison trigger on him.

06:52.590 --> 06:53.520
Poison trigger?

07:03.950 --> 07:06.680
The Empress Dowager has passed away!

07:09.120 --> 07:12.160
The Empress Dowager has passed away!

07:10.340 --> 07:15.100
[Taiji Hall]

07:17.660 --> 07:19.720
The Empress Dowager has passed away!

07:20.420 --> 07:22.480
The Empress Dowager has passed away!

07:23.000 --> 07:25.060
The Empress Dowager has passed away!

07:25.560 --> 07:27.620
The Empress Dowager has passed away!

07:28.160 --> 07:30.220
The Empress Dowager has passed away!

07:41.310 --> 07:41.770
Wanyin.

07:43.960 --> 07:44.770
You're awake.

07:47.240 --> 07:48.700
Does your head still hurt?

07:51.190 --> 07:51.890
Are you all right?

07:51.890 --> 07:52.480
I'm fine.

07:53.120 --> 07:54.850
That powder wasn't poisonous.

07:55.560 --> 07:56.420
Not poisonous?

08:00.820 --> 08:02.220
Then why did I...

08:02.510 --> 08:03.910
Xie Yong'er reminded me.

08:04.270 --> 08:06.870
Do you remember what the Empress Dowager
said before she died?

08:06.870 --> 08:09.270
That she regretted using the wrong poison.

08:09.930 --> 08:11.260
I think she did say that.

08:11.360 --> 08:13.480
It was my bad luck.

08:13.600 --> 08:16.540
I chose the wrong poison.

08:16.690 --> 08:18.680
There are two parts to a poison:
the seed and the trigger.

08:18.680 --> 08:20.270
The Empress Dowager must have planted

08:20.270 --> 08:22.270
the poison seed when you were young.

08:22.720 --> 08:23.190
Later,

08:24.240 --> 08:25.570
she would periodically

08:26.160 --> 08:28.290
administer the poison trigger on you,

08:28.480 --> 08:30.610
gradually worsening your headaches,

08:30.750 --> 08:33.200
making you unable
to control your emotions,

08:33.200 --> 08:36.059
and turning you into
the tyrant everyone speaks of.

08:37.030 --> 08:38.390
You mean

08:40.059 --> 08:42.179
what the Crown Prince sprinkled
was a poison trigger?

08:42.179 --> 08:42.710
Exactly.

08:43.789 --> 08:45.800
That's why even though
I inhaled most of it,

08:45.800 --> 08:47.000
I remained unharmed.

08:47.550 --> 08:48.840
But you only came in contact
with a little,

08:48.840 --> 08:50.300
and immediately acted up.

08:51.900 --> 08:53.150
I just don't know

08:53.750 --> 08:55.880
how she planted the poison seed in you.

08:59.790 --> 09:00.830
Empress Ci Zhen

09:01.600 --> 09:04.130
had a very difficult time
during childbirth.

09:06.610 --> 09:08.340
I fear I was born with it.

09:15.360 --> 09:17.230
So Xiahou Dan's fate...

09:21.000 --> 09:23.000
was written before he was even born.

09:26.270 --> 09:28.000
So all my struggles

09:30.670 --> 09:31.730
were meaningless.

09:34.480 --> 09:36.080
But he met you and me,

09:36.750 --> 09:38.350
so it wasn't all for nothing.

09:39.510 --> 09:41.320
We've narrowed down the poison's origin

09:41.320 --> 09:42.510
to the Qiang State.

09:43.130 --> 09:43.970
Finding it

09:44.630 --> 09:45.960
is just a matter of time.

09:57.440 --> 09:58.030
Wanyin.

09:59.600 --> 10:00.240
Thank you.

10:07.360 --> 10:09.690
On behalf of this unfortunate Xiahou Dan,

10:11.510 --> 10:12.120
thank you.

10:18.510 --> 10:20.240
With the Empress Dowager dead,

10:21.210 --> 10:22.700
Prince Duan's next target

10:23.750 --> 10:24.600
will be us.

10:26.350 --> 10:28.080
I forgot to tell you yesterday.

10:29.320 --> 10:30.720
News came from the border

10:31.480 --> 10:33.610
that all three armies are mobilizing.

10:33.790 --> 10:35.120
What we feared has come.

10:35.320 --> 10:37.380
Our worst suspicions are confirmed.

10:38.630 --> 10:39.360
So,

10:40.240 --> 10:42.840
before Prince Duan's reinforcements
arrive,

10:42.930 --> 10:44.660
the Empress Dowager's funeral

10:45.390 --> 10:46.450
must be expedited.

10:47.770 --> 10:50.840
The Azure Dragon of the East,
the White Tiger of the West,

10:50.840 --> 10:53.960
the Vermilion Bird of the South,
and the Black Turtle of the North—

10:53.960 --> 10:57.750
each of these four celestial guardians
has seven mansions beneath them.

10:57.750 --> 11:01.360
Unfortunately, they all have conflicts
with the Empress Dowager's burial date.

11:01.360 --> 11:05.030
Even though the Empress Dowager
led a diligent life full of blessings,

11:05.030 --> 11:07.410
we should not go against heaven's will

11:07.720 --> 11:09.000
and disturb her peace.

11:09.080 --> 11:12.360
This newly appointed
Imperial Astronomer Director

11:12.550 --> 11:14.710
speaks quite like Yang.

11:14.810 --> 11:16.080
Of course.

11:16.550 --> 11:18.240
I wrote this speech.

11:18.320 --> 11:20.000
Didn't you transfer
to the Ministry of Personnel?

11:20.000 --> 11:23.200
Why are you still
handling the Imperial Astronomer's affairs?

11:23.200 --> 11:24.620
It's just a small favor.

11:24.790 --> 11:25.990
Her Highness calls it

11:26.030 --> 11:27.160
resource exchange.

11:27.630 --> 11:28.240
Besides,

11:28.390 --> 11:30.270
what if I need the Imperial Astronomy's
help in the future?

11:30.270 --> 11:31.030
After

11:31.360 --> 11:32.690
my careful calculation

11:33.000 --> 11:34.330
and thorough analysis,

11:34.390 --> 11:35.850
I have finally determined

11:36.440 --> 11:38.150
that the 14th day of the 11th Lunar Month

11:38.150 --> 11:41.080
is an auspicious day
that comes once in a hundred years.

11:41.080 --> 11:42.270
It's suitable for burial,

11:42.270 --> 11:43.400
opening the coffin,

11:43.440 --> 11:44.500
moving the casket,

11:44.870 --> 11:46.730
receiving ancestral blessings,

11:47.030 --> 11:49.910
and protecting future generations.

11:55.840 --> 11:56.910
Good!

11:57.030 --> 11:58.100
A good day indeed!

11:58.360 --> 11:59.920
An auspicious day!

12:02.010 --> 12:05.270
The 14th of the 11th Lunar Month
is just three days from now.

12:05.790 --> 12:07.510
Isn't this a bit too rushed?

12:10.270 --> 12:11.030
Mr. Chen,

12:12.070 --> 12:13.600
do you have any objections?

12:14.360 --> 12:15.820
I have none, Your Majesty.

12:18.440 --> 12:20.630
Since none of you have any objections,

12:21.160 --> 12:22.560
we shall proceed with

12:24.390 --> 12:26.150
the Empress Dowager's burial
in three days.

12:26.150 --> 12:28.240
Your Majesty is wise.

12:35.870 --> 12:37.470
[Compendium of Rare Poisons]

12:40.080 --> 12:41.480
This one should be lower.

12:41.670 --> 12:42.520
Yes, lower.

12:44.870 --> 12:46.730
Arrange the fruit plates evenly.

12:48.870 --> 12:49.580
Bring that in.

12:49.580 --> 12:49.960
Come.

12:50.870 --> 12:51.200
What?

12:58.730 --> 12:59.190
Done.

13:07.600 --> 13:11.490
♪ When the net of destiny
blocks the light ♪

13:11.850 --> 13:14.160
♪ Floating in the trap ♪

13:16.000 --> 13:17.080
This is my first time seeing

13:16.280 --> 13:17.730
♪ It's like a mystery ♪

13:17.790 --> 13:19.320
this place when it's empty.

13:19.340 --> 13:23.470
♪ But with the ending not yet determined ♪

13:20.440 --> 13:22.500
You didn't have to accompany me here.

13:23.920 --> 13:26.510
♪ No one can define me ♪

13:27.510 --> 13:29.080
I used to hate every brick

13:28.210 --> 13:30.060
♪ My whole life ♪

13:29.480 --> 13:30.240
here.

13:31.180 --> 13:34.190
♪ Standing in the hurricane,
watching the fire rise ♪

13:32.110 --> 13:32.910
But now,

13:34.440 --> 13:35.510
with the person I despised gone,

13:34.520 --> 13:37.250
♪ Dancing on the blade's edge, I thread
through blood, writing my wild ode ♪

13:37.200 --> 13:38.120
these things

13:37.460 --> 13:38.460
♪ I am not one of the gentle ones ♪

13:38.480 --> 13:42.010
♪ How could my thoughts
be tethered to the soft begonia?  ♪

13:39.600 --> 13:41.330
don't seem so hateful anymore.

13:43.280 --> 13:44.790
♪ Do not speak to me
of what's inappropriate ♪

13:44.820 --> 13:46.280
♪ I am the moral order ♪

13:46.000 --> 13:47.000
With the Empress Dowager dead

13:46.520 --> 13:49.320
♪ The gleam of the blade
tempers feathers into a phantom Phoenix  ♪

13:47.950 --> 13:49.480
and her faction disbanded,

13:49.550 --> 13:50.500
♪ And these Phoenix bones of mine ♪

13:50.520 --> 13:55.390
♪ Empower me
to pierce through the wind and waves ♪

13:51.080 --> 13:53.140
no one will feed these birds anymore.

13:54.670 --> 13:56.000
If we don't set them free,

13:56.000 --> 13:56.820
they'll starve to death.

13:56.820 --> 13:58.430
♪ Allow me ♪

13:58.490 --> 14:01.080
♪ To not linger in shame,
to not give way ♪

14:01.530 --> 14:04.000
♪ To not be faithless,
to not admit defeat ♪

14:04.500 --> 14:07.350
♪ A body of stubborn pride
rises to shout that I ♪

14:04.510 --> 14:05.440
You're free now.

14:05.830 --> 14:06.540
Fly away!

14:07.460 --> 14:09.940
♪ Was never a creature
meant for the shallows ♪

14:09.370 --> 14:10.660
Birds with clipped wings

14:10.470 --> 14:11.510
♪ Allow me ♪

14:11.440 --> 14:12.600
have long forgotten how to fly.

14:11.750 --> 14:13.110
♪ To never pause ♪

14:13.430 --> 14:14.500
♪ Allow me ♪

14:14.810 --> 14:16.160
♪ To dare to shatter my bones ♪

14:16.360 --> 14:25.780
♪ Wherever I stand,
I dare to write a legend of glory ♪

14:16.630 --> 14:17.030
Fly!

14:18.240 --> 14:18.970
Come on, fly!

14:24.150 --> 14:24.480
Come.

14:25.940 --> 14:26.870
Don't be afraid.

14:32.630 --> 14:32.960
Come.

14:37.230 --> 14:40.140
♪ Standing in the hurricane,
watching the fire rise ♪

14:40.490 --> 14:43.260
♪ Dancing on the blade's edge, I thread
through blood, writing my wild ode ♪

14:43.520 --> 14:44.340
♪ I am not one of the gentle ones ♪

14:44.430 --> 14:47.990
♪ How could my thoughts
be tethered to the soft begonia?  ♪

14:49.260 --> 14:50.790
♪ Do not speak to me
of what's inappropriate ♪

14:49.330 --> 14:50.580
Cut wings

14:50.810 --> 14:52.260
♪ I am the moral order ♪

14:51.520 --> 14:52.940
will grow back eventually.

14:52.520 --> 14:55.330
♪ The gleam of the blade
tempers feathers into a phantom Phoenix  ♪

14:55.000 --> 14:56.390
Flying is a bird's nature.

14:55.490 --> 14:56.520
♪ And these Phoenix bones of mine ♪

14:56.600 --> 15:01.440
♪ Empower me
to pierce through the wind and waves ♪

14:57.360 --> 14:59.020
No matter how long it's caged,

14:59.670 --> 15:01.130
it will never forget that.

15:02.850 --> 15:04.560
♪ Allow me ♪

15:04.520 --> 15:05.090
Fly.

15:04.580 --> 15:07.110
♪ To not linger in shame,
to not give way ♪

15:07.500 --> 15:09.990
♪ To not be faithless,
to not admit defeat ♪

15:09.750 --> 15:10.140
Fly.

15:10.440 --> 15:13.360
♪ A body of stubborn pride
rises to shout that I ♪

15:11.150 --> 15:11.630
See.

15:13.470 --> 15:15.970
♪ Was never a creature
meant for the shallows ♪

15:13.480 --> 15:14.200
I told you.

15:16.380 --> 15:17.540
♪ Allow me ♪

15:17.770 --> 15:19.120
♪ To never pause ♪

15:19.150 --> 15:20.480
♪ Allow me ♪

15:20.730 --> 15:22.130
♪ To dare to shatter my bones ♪

15:22.410 --> 15:30.410
♪ Wherever I stand,
I dare to write a legend of glory ♪

15:26.830 --> 15:27.960
You're free now.

15:37.600 --> 15:38.400
Thank you

15:38.840 --> 15:41.040
for taking care of so many things for me.

15:42.030 --> 15:43.000
What's with you?

15:43.080 --> 15:44.680
Why so polite all of a sudden?

15:47.200 --> 15:48.440
It's just too cold.

15:49.120 --> 15:50.380
How can it be this cold?

15:51.960 --> 15:54.240
Don't you feel the chilly draft here?

15:56.390 --> 15:56.990
Take this.

15:58.630 --> 15:59.420
Take it.

15:59.670 --> 16:00.070
Quick.

16:06.600 --> 16:08.130
After kneeling for so long,

16:08.150 --> 16:10.480
how is your hot water bottle
still so warm?

16:11.230 --> 16:13.830
I added a layer of tin foil inside.

16:14.320 --> 16:15.450
Don't you remember?

16:15.480 --> 16:16.790
The takeout food from our world

16:16.790 --> 16:17.920
always arrives hot.

16:19.630 --> 16:20.840
You're so clever.

16:20.960 --> 16:23.020
No wonder you could kneel for so long.

16:26.720 --> 16:27.580
Your Highness.

16:28.770 --> 16:30.170
May I have a word with you?

16:45.440 --> 16:46.040
What is it?

16:49.150 --> 16:50.010
Your Highness,

16:50.030 --> 16:51.030
I have failed you.

16:51.600 --> 16:53.750
I've searched through all of
the Imperial Medical Bureau's books

16:53.750 --> 16:57.350
but still couldn't identify
the exact components of the poison.

16:59.150 --> 16:59.980
I knew it.

17:00.960 --> 17:03.120
Whenever someone asks
for a word in private,

17:03.120 --> 17:04.800
it's rarely good news.

17:06.109 --> 17:07.970
But I haven't come empty-handed.

17:09.200 --> 17:10.130
Physician Xiao,

17:10.480 --> 17:12.410
please tell me everything at once.

17:13.589 --> 17:15.250
My apologies, Your Highness.

17:16.589 --> 17:19.030
The poison His Majesty was exposed to
at Mount Bei

17:19.030 --> 17:21.690
should have prevented
his wounds from healing,

17:21.920 --> 17:24.050
yet he recovered remarkably quickly.

17:25.069 --> 17:27.240
This time,
while most of the poison trigger

17:27.240 --> 17:29.920
the Crown Prince released this time
was inhaled by Your Highness,

17:29.920 --> 17:32.320
His Majesty still inhaled more than usual.

17:33.200 --> 17:34.130
Yet the headache

17:34.270 --> 17:36.080
only occurred once that night.

17:36.510 --> 17:37.170
Therefore,

17:37.830 --> 17:39.030
I have a bold idea.

17:39.550 --> 17:40.550
Please continue.

17:40.750 --> 17:42.110
Your Highness mentioned

17:42.110 --> 17:43.920
fighting poison with poison last time,

17:43.920 --> 17:45.160
which from a medical perspective

17:45.160 --> 17:45.890
is feasible.

17:46.790 --> 17:48.090
So if we can find

17:48.510 --> 17:51.640
a poison that counteracts
the one in His Majesty's body,

17:51.640 --> 17:53.300
I have a 50% chance of success.

17:55.790 --> 17:56.590
I understand.

17:57.550 --> 17:59.060
I'll send a message by carrier pigeon

17:59.060 --> 18:00.790
and ask Tu'er to help us search.

18:01.590 --> 18:03.120
I hope there's enough time.

18:06.920 --> 18:09.180
Your Highness's devotion to His Majesty

18:09.200 --> 18:10.460
will move the heavens.

18:10.640 --> 18:12.300
I'm sure we'll make it in time.

18:13.400 --> 18:15.480
Physician Xiao,
you've always been straightforward.

18:15.480 --> 18:17.140
But now you're flattering me?

18:22.110 --> 18:24.110
Physician Xiao, what are you doing?

18:24.550 --> 18:25.410
Your Highness,

18:26.030 --> 18:26.720
I dare

18:27.440 --> 18:29.440
to make a request of you.

18:30.270 --> 18:30.800
Go ahead.

18:33.920 --> 18:36.270
I see His Majesty trusts you greatly.

18:37.750 --> 18:38.750
After His Majesty

18:39.160 --> 18:41.290
resolves the matter with Prince Duan,

18:41.310 --> 18:42.440
could Your Highness

18:42.480 --> 18:44.420
put in a good word with His Majesty

18:45.240 --> 18:46.010
and ask him

18:46.920 --> 18:49.130
to release Consort Xie?

18:49.920 --> 18:50.580
You mean...

18:52.070 --> 18:53.270
You mean Xie Yong'er?

18:56.200 --> 18:56.800
You two...

18:57.750 --> 18:59.480
Your Highness, please don't misunderstand.

18:59.480 --> 19:01.510
My relationship with Consort Xie
is completely innocent.

19:01.510 --> 19:03.030
It's just that day in the flower house,

19:03.030 --> 19:04.630
when I first met Consort Xie,

19:04.750 --> 19:06.080
she showed me kindness.

19:06.400 --> 19:08.260
She is such a wise and kind person.

19:08.790 --> 19:10.070
I truly cannot bear

19:10.640 --> 19:13.170
to see her wither
like those angelica plants,

19:13.310 --> 19:14.310
fading day by day.

19:16.230 --> 19:16.890
Therefore,

19:17.480 --> 19:17.920
I beg

19:19.160 --> 19:20.640
Your Highness to help her.

19:22.350 --> 19:24.010
Physician Xiao, please rise.

19:24.920 --> 19:26.380
Thank you, Your Highness.

19:26.510 --> 19:27.750
Yong'er is fortunate

19:28.880 --> 19:30.280
to have a friend like you.

19:35.070 --> 19:35.800
Don't worry.

19:36.720 --> 19:38.580
We're thinking of the same thing.

19:40.720 --> 19:43.160
On the day of
the Empress Dowager's funeral,

19:43.160 --> 19:46.070
after Prince Duan follows
the funeral procession out of the city,

19:46.070 --> 19:47.270
I will send people to escort her

19:47.270 --> 19:49.930
to leave the capital
in the opposite direction.

19:50.400 --> 19:51.130
By that time,

19:52.400 --> 19:54.600
it will be too late
for Prince Duan to find her.

19:54.600 --> 19:55.530
The Emperor and I

19:56.310 --> 19:59.110
don't know if we can
ultimately defeat Prince Duan.

19:59.110 --> 20:00.960
So every additional day
Yong'er stays in this palace

20:00.960 --> 20:02.360
is another day of danger.

20:02.920 --> 20:04.450
Only by leaving this palace

20:04.680 --> 20:05.880
can she truly be safe.

20:07.400 --> 20:10.200
So Your Majesty
and Your Highness have already...

20:11.880 --> 20:12.610
I am ashamed.

20:13.550 --> 20:14.000
I

20:15.070 --> 20:16.730
will do everything in my power

20:16.750 --> 20:18.610
to protect His Majesty from harm.

20:20.480 --> 20:22.340
You've reminded me of something.

20:25.030 --> 20:26.740
Since parting is inevitable,

20:28.680 --> 20:30.010
then her final memories

20:31.000 --> 20:33.330
shouldn't just be the warmth in her hands.

20:47.440 --> 20:49.040
What did Physician Xiao say?

20:50.310 --> 20:51.830
Today is the winter solstice.

20:51.830 --> 20:53.090
Do you want dumplings?

20:53.720 --> 20:54.640
Dumplings?

20:57.380 --> 20:59.770
Your Majesty!

20:59.880 --> 21:03.640
Why did you leave me?

21:13.790 --> 21:15.910
Her Majesty has fainted from grief.

21:16.040 --> 21:18.300
Someone help take her back to the palace!

21:31.880 --> 21:33.020
This is just dough.

21:33.100 --> 21:35.360
You can only wrap it after rolling it out.

21:37.960 --> 21:39.720
What is this?

21:41.790 --> 21:42.940
My buns.

21:43.160 --> 21:44.310
They're better than yours.

21:44.310 --> 21:45.110
Look at yours.

21:45.310 --> 21:46.310
The filling's coming out.

21:46.310 --> 21:47.030
So what?

21:47.110 --> 21:48.480
Don't you think it's novel?

21:48.480 --> 21:48.940
Well...

21:51.550 --> 21:52.680
I'm better than you.

21:54.960 --> 21:55.740
How so?

21:56.030 --> 21:58.090
Given how I know my own incompetency.

21:58.830 --> 21:59.630
You know what?

21:59.830 --> 22:00.830
It looks like you.

22:00.880 --> 22:02.940
But I did it according to how you look.

22:03.550 --> 22:03.960
Stop!

22:04.640 --> 22:05.360
All of you!

22:05.680 --> 22:06.990
Get out of here.

22:07.010 --> 22:08.670
Stop wasting my ingredients!

22:10.750 --> 22:12.410
Everyone out! Did you hear me?

22:12.420 --> 22:12.880
Move it!

22:26.680 --> 22:27.830
This fish is not for eating.

22:27.830 --> 22:29.160
You can look at it but not eat it.

22:29.160 --> 22:30.510
It symbolizes abundance.

22:30.510 --> 22:31.110
Is that so?

22:31.480 --> 22:32.750
Come, have some dumplings.

22:32.750 --> 22:32.960
Here.

22:32.960 --> 22:33.480
Have some dumplings.

22:33.480 --> 22:33.960
Try them.

22:33.960 --> 22:35.160
What filling is this?

22:35.540 --> 22:37.070
What filling don't you eat?

22:37.440 --> 22:38.310
I don't eat pork.

22:38.310 --> 22:38.910
It's pork.

22:41.400 --> 22:42.460
It's beef filling.

22:43.830 --> 22:44.490
Delicious.

22:46.000 --> 22:46.480
Cen,

22:46.960 --> 22:47.510
it's hot.

22:48.200 --> 22:49.310
Today is the winter solstice.

22:49.310 --> 22:51.110
Have a drink to warm yourself up.

22:51.240 --> 22:51.840
All right.

22:53.590 --> 22:54.060
Come on.

22:54.310 --> 22:54.790
Well...

22:55.510 --> 22:56.770
We're together again.

22:57.680 --> 22:59.840
I wish Cen good health.

23:00.350 --> 23:01.400
And a speedy recovery.

23:01.400 --> 23:03.530
Thank you for your hospitality today.

23:03.680 --> 23:05.040
Thank you, Er Lan.

23:05.590 --> 23:06.450
Come, drink up.

23:13.720 --> 23:14.580
Have some more.

23:15.200 --> 23:16.750
One cup is enough.

23:17.790 --> 23:18.790
Er, you…

23:19.880 --> 23:22.280
why are you acting
like a controlling wife?

23:22.830 --> 23:23.750
Yang,

23:23.960 --> 23:26.200
you haven't even started drinking
and you're already talking nonsense.

23:26.200 --> 23:27.510
Today is the winter solstice.

23:27.510 --> 23:29.440
We should drink until we're drunk.

23:29.920 --> 23:30.550
Besides,

23:32.640 --> 23:34.840
Er's cooking skills are so impressive.

23:35.640 --> 23:37.790
He can serve in court
and cook in the kitchen.

23:37.790 --> 23:39.160
If you were a woman,

23:39.310 --> 23:42.110
countless families
would be lining up to propose.

23:42.720 --> 23:44.750
Yang, what's gotten into you today?

23:45.350 --> 23:46.640
-Why? Don't like hearing what I'm saying?
-Stop drinking.

23:46.640 --> 23:47.160
That's enough, don't drink anymore.

23:47.160 --> 23:48.070
Come on, stop drinking for now.

23:48.070 --> 23:49.130
What's the matter?

23:50.750 --> 23:51.920
If you want to marry someone

23:51.920 --> 23:53.730
just because she's good at cooking

23:53.730 --> 23:56.030
rather than
for her personality and talents,

23:56.030 --> 23:57.830
you might as well remain single.

23:57.960 --> 23:58.830
Li is right.

23:59.510 --> 24:01.310
When it comes to knowledge and wisdom,

24:01.310 --> 24:02.640
gender doesn't matter;

24:02.960 --> 24:04.160
only ability counts.

24:06.200 --> 24:06.690
Er.

24:07.470 --> 24:09.070
Being a good cook is useless.

24:09.770 --> 24:10.780
Can't you tell?

24:11.140 --> 24:12.270
He's insulting you.

24:12.960 --> 24:13.580
Is that so?

24:13.680 --> 24:15.080
Quite a harsh insult too.

24:15.640 --> 24:16.570
Hey, Cen, you...

24:18.030 --> 24:19.490
See? He's half recovered.

24:19.610 --> 24:20.950
Give me back my wine.

24:22.270 --> 24:22.600
Here.

24:25.270 --> 24:26.200
Drink your wine.

24:27.710 --> 24:29.370
Come on, let me pour it for you.

24:34.030 --> 24:34.560
General!

24:34.880 --> 24:35.410
General!

24:35.620 --> 24:37.950
There's an urgent confidential message.

24:43.260 --> 24:45.840
[The Empress Dowager's funeral will be
held on the 14th of the 11th Lunar Month]

24:45.860 --> 24:48.050
[The advance party has gathered
at Mount Bei. The remaining troops]

24:48.070 --> 24:49.920
[will arrive at the city gates in 5 days
to intimidate the Royalists.]

24:54.240 --> 24:54.830
I knew it.

24:56.270 --> 24:58.000
Once the Empress Dowager dies,

24:58.350 --> 25:00.750
Prince Duan would certainly make his move.

25:02.070 --> 25:02.830
This kingdom

25:04.510 --> 25:06.110
will likely fall into chaos.

25:06.880 --> 25:07.490
General,

25:07.720 --> 25:08.460
should our Right Army

25:08.460 --> 25:10.390
still be moving around in stealth?

25:13.350 --> 25:14.750
Is that still necessary?

25:16.560 --> 25:18.820
All three armies are already on the move.

25:20.200 --> 25:22.160
It's just a matter of who's faster now.

25:22.160 --> 25:24.620
Dumplings with wine bring more prosperity.

25:24.640 --> 25:27.000
Dumplings with fish
bring abundance every year.

25:27.000 --> 25:28.510
One should hold the dumpling bowl
on the winter solstice.

25:28.510 --> 25:30.840
Otherwise, you will freeze off your ears!

25:32.430 --> 25:32.830
Here.

25:33.000 --> 25:33.920
Thank you, Mr. Bei.

25:33.920 --> 25:34.720
Thank you.

25:35.070 --> 25:36.200
Time for dumplings!

25:37.640 --> 25:37.920
Eat.

25:40.510 --> 25:41.570
Thank you, Mr. Bei.

25:47.350 --> 25:48.810
I just bit onto something.

25:48.960 --> 25:49.760
What's wrong?

25:55.550 --> 25:56.550
That's good luck!

25:57.270 --> 25:58.190
I wish

25:58.270 --> 25:59.510
everything goes as you wish

25:59.510 --> 26:00.970
and peace year after year!

26:02.200 --> 26:02.660
Mr. Bei.

26:04.550 --> 26:06.070
I pay you respects as your junior.

26:06.070 --> 26:07.560
Wishing you good health

26:07.590 --> 26:09.030
and success in everything
in the coming year.

26:09.030 --> 26:10.160
You shouldn't, you shouldn't.

26:10.160 --> 26:11.530
It's fine, Mr. Bei.

26:11.640 --> 26:12.500
Just accept it.

26:23.640 --> 26:24.590
I found one too!

26:26.380 --> 26:26.960
Yong'er.

26:28.200 --> 26:29.290
Then we wish you

26:29.350 --> 26:30.590
a smooth departure from the palace

26:30.590 --> 26:32.520
to see the world and find yourself.

26:33.200 --> 26:33.930
Thank you.

26:34.510 --> 26:35.240
Xie Yong'er.

26:35.510 --> 26:36.370
I thank you too.

26:37.310 --> 26:38.640
All these talks are useless.

26:38.640 --> 26:39.950
When I leave the palace,

26:39.950 --> 26:41.810
just give me enough travel money.

26:43.440 --> 26:44.100
My turn now.

26:44.350 --> 26:45.350
Do I have one too?

26:50.830 --> 26:51.560
Is there one?

26:56.670 --> 26:57.470
Wait, Mr. Bei,

26:57.590 --> 26:59.520
how many coins did you put in total?

27:00.690 --> 27:02.420
There's one in every dumpling.

27:04.140 --> 27:05.140
Luck is something

27:05.240 --> 27:06.640
you need to make yourself

27:07.350 --> 27:08.250
if you want it.

27:09.780 --> 27:10.820
Then eat more.

27:10.920 --> 27:13.250
All your travel money is in the dumplings.

27:13.590 --> 27:14.650
What a cheapskate!

27:17.170 --> 27:18.100
It's delicious.

27:19.960 --> 27:20.430
Eat up.

27:21.400 --> 27:24.320
[Tablet of the Mother of the Prince, Li]

27:53.510 --> 27:53.970
Mother.

27:54.230 --> 27:55.630
The dumplings are ready.

27:58.870 --> 27:59.710
Look at you.

27:59.810 --> 28:01.610
You got flour all over your face.

28:01.780 --> 28:02.380
Come here.

28:02.840 --> 28:04.500
You look like a little kitten.

28:11.030 --> 28:11.490
Mother.

28:11.890 --> 28:12.550
You eat.

28:13.920 --> 28:14.780
You eat first.

28:22.160 --> 28:22.890
Mother.

28:23.590 --> 28:24.830
What are you embroidering?

28:24.830 --> 28:26.760
I'm embroidering a sachet for you.

28:27.680 --> 28:29.000
May it bless you

28:29.310 --> 28:31.110
and keep you healthy every year.

28:39.750 --> 28:40.420
Mother.

28:42.030 --> 28:44.380
You've been gone for 14 years.

28:48.610 --> 28:50.350
I think about you every day.

28:55.040 --> 28:57.460
The sachet you embroidered for me,

29:01.360 --> 29:02.950
I wear it every day.

29:15.140 --> 29:16.740
Mother, please bless me with

29:18.440 --> 29:20.280
triumph and success

29:22.510 --> 29:23.790
tomorrow.

29:31.110 --> 29:33.000
What do you want to do
after leaving the palace?

29:33.000 --> 29:35.260
I want to travel and see the sights first,

29:35.640 --> 29:37.880
then explore this world properly.

29:39.640 --> 29:40.680
And then...

29:41.480 --> 29:42.540
live in seclusion?

29:42.640 --> 29:43.850
No way!

29:44.240 --> 29:46.110
I want to wait
until you've stabilized the country,

29:46.110 --> 29:47.910
then get some royal investment.

29:48.790 --> 29:49.720
What do you think

29:49.750 --> 29:51.830
about me starting a business empire?

29:52.350 --> 29:53.510
Look at you.

29:53.790 --> 29:54.990
Truly the chosen one.

29:56.350 --> 29:58.410
Do you have specific business plans?

29:59.720 --> 30:02.050
I plan to develop a food delivery service,

30:02.510 --> 30:04.840
starting with the city
as the foundation.

30:04.960 --> 30:05.750
That's a good one.

30:05.750 --> 30:06.950
I want to invest in it!

30:06.960 --> 30:08.890
We could also do package delivery.

30:08.960 --> 30:10.180
But transportation

30:10.510 --> 30:11.750
is inadequate in this world.

30:11.750 --> 30:13.010
We need to build roads.

30:13.080 --> 30:14.520
If I were to make cars,

30:14.880 --> 30:15.880
would you invest?

30:17.480 --> 30:19.110
Why not go all the way

30:19.350 --> 30:21.240
and build a maglev tube system?

30:21.350 --> 30:22.660
Maglev?

30:23.350 --> 30:24.100
What's that?

30:24.850 --> 30:25.670
Oh no,

30:25.920 --> 30:27.600
when "Devil's Favorite Concubine"
was published,

30:27.600 --> 30:29.660
maglev tubes didn't exist, did they?

30:30.070 --> 30:32.580
I read about it in sci-fi novels.

30:32.680 --> 30:34.280
I can't explain it properly.

30:35.070 --> 30:37.480
You want me to build something
from sci-fi novels?

30:37.480 --> 30:38.940
You think too highly of me.

30:39.960 --> 30:41.200
I'm just kidding.

30:44.590 --> 30:45.790
You mentioned before

30:46.030 --> 30:47.790
that in your world,
you lived in...

30:47.790 --> 30:48.850
Where was it again?

30:49.720 --> 30:50.350
Bei...

30:51.440 --> 30:51.960
Bei...

30:51.960 --> 30:53.360
Just a small county town.

30:54.160 --> 30:55.820
You wouldn't have heard of it.

30:58.570 --> 30:59.170
All right.

31:01.170 --> 31:01.770
By the way,

31:02.590 --> 31:03.490
remember to

31:03.790 --> 31:04.980
pass this letter to Xiao Tiancai

31:03.990 --> 31:07.250
[To Xiao Tiancai]

31:05.200 --> 31:06.530
after I leave tomorrow.

31:10.000 --> 31:11.530
You're friend-zoning him?

31:14.200 --> 31:16.130
You're really friend-zoning him?

31:16.640 --> 31:17.960
Don't make our dear Physician Xiao

31:17.960 --> 31:19.590
so upset that he goes on strike.

31:19.590 --> 31:21.460
It's not friend-zoning him.

31:21.640 --> 31:23.490
I told you we're just friends.

31:24.200 --> 31:25.600
You're overthinking it.

31:26.720 --> 31:27.140
Fine.

31:27.830 --> 31:29.030
I'll pass this to him.

31:34.160 --> 31:34.830
Thank you.

31:36.160 --> 31:37.020
I never thought

31:37.920 --> 31:39.590
the person I'd entrust something to

31:39.590 --> 31:40.850
would be you in the end.

31:46.510 --> 31:47.560
This plot

31:47.880 --> 31:49.740
is like a wild horse running free.

31:51.270 --> 31:52.470
At this point of time,

31:53.110 --> 31:55.310
I really don't know where it's heading.

31:55.920 --> 31:57.320
I'm not surprised at all.

31:58.400 --> 32:00.400
We're from the same place after all.

32:00.790 --> 32:02.650
We're like a mirror in this world.

32:06.160 --> 32:06.960
That's right.

32:08.350 --> 32:09.610
I finally understand.

32:10.310 --> 32:11.350
In this world,

32:13.000 --> 32:15.530
having someone who understands me
like you do

32:15.550 --> 32:16.550
isn't dangerous

32:18.980 --> 32:19.910
but comforting.

32:23.680 --> 32:25.070
Sis...

32:28.880 --> 32:30.340
You're being so dramatic.

32:39.200 --> 32:39.830
All right.

32:41.400 --> 32:42.130
I'm leaving.

32:42.830 --> 32:44.160
Don't forget to miss me.

33:06.790 --> 33:07.310
Wanyin!

33:11.830 --> 33:12.820
It's a deal.

33:13.790 --> 33:16.070
When I get my food delivery business
up and running,

33:16.070 --> 33:17.450
you'll teach me

33:17.510 --> 33:19.830
some specialty snacks from your hometown.

33:19.830 --> 33:20.370
Sure!

33:50.270 --> 33:51.130
Your Highness.

33:55.730 --> 33:56.590
Your Highness.

34:07.440 --> 34:08.610
Go and prepare.

34:09.000 --> 34:09.320
Yes.

34:14.840 --> 34:15.239
Leave!

34:37.330 --> 34:38.560
I once said

34:41.290 --> 34:44.620
to prevent them from using foresight
to predict the future,

34:45.760 --> 34:46.989
at a critical moment,

34:47.940 --> 34:49.739
I would insert a small variable.

34:52.150 --> 34:53.800
Now, that moment has come.

35:15.960 --> 35:16.710
These

35:17.250 --> 35:19.030
were truly written by Consort Yu?

35:19.030 --> 35:19.830
That's right.

35:21.400 --> 35:22.650
Even this sachet

35:23.820 --> 35:26.020
was embroidered for me by her own hands.

35:30.840 --> 35:32.070
What I'm about to say,

35:32.710 --> 35:34.920
you must remember word for word.

35:38.070 --> 35:40.360
That year at the Lantern Festival
flower market,

35:40.360 --> 35:41.220
she was dressed

35:41.390 --> 35:43.050
fully in plain white clothes,

35:43.990 --> 35:46.920
yet her breathtaking beauty
could not be concealed.

35:47.190 --> 35:49.850
At that time,
she had not yet entered the palace.

35:51.110 --> 35:52.570
You two were deeply in love

35:53.440 --> 35:55.440
and exchanged tokens of affection.

35:56.320 --> 35:57.150
You thought

35:57.630 --> 35:59.690
you would marry her and bring her home

35:59.800 --> 36:01.000
to grow old together.

36:01.400 --> 36:03.530
But who could have imagined her father

36:04.000 --> 36:06.000
was a vain man.

36:08.400 --> 36:09.710
For his own career,

36:11.360 --> 36:13.360
he sent his daughter into the palace

36:14.040 --> 36:15.440
to become a consort.

36:16.940 --> 36:19.400
From then on,
separated by the palace walls,

36:20.480 --> 36:22.610
you could not ease the pain of longing.

36:24.120 --> 36:26.250
However, this woman was quite clever.

36:27.650 --> 36:29.980
She became the Emperor's favored consort

36:31.590 --> 36:32.910
and used some methods

36:33.770 --> 36:36.970
to have you promoted to
Commander of the Imperial Guards.

36:38.440 --> 36:39.230
From then on,

36:40.540 --> 36:43.310
you had some convenient means to meet.

36:46.590 --> 36:47.990
But you were not content—

36:50.170 --> 36:52.770
not content to sneak around forever
like this.

36:55.020 --> 36:55.830
Moreover,

36:57.550 --> 36:59.410
she was pregnant with your child.

37:08.760 --> 37:09.910
Such words

37:11.590 --> 37:12.740
will cost me my life.

37:14.550 --> 37:16.150
If you are unwilling,

37:18.170 --> 37:20.790
I can send you out of the city tonight.

37:21.840 --> 37:23.580
To live out your days

37:24.610 --> 37:26.940
in a remote manor
doesn't sound bad at all.

37:28.150 --> 37:29.950
Your Highness misunderstands.

37:32.190 --> 37:34.540
Rather than live like a rat in the gutter,

37:36.030 --> 37:37.430
I'd rather take a gamble.

37:38.800 --> 37:40.530
I'm betting that Your Highness

37:41.590 --> 37:43.540
is the one chosen by destiny.

37:45.840 --> 37:47.110
But will the Emperor

37:48.540 --> 37:49.950
really buy this story?

37:53.030 --> 37:54.960
Whether he buys it doesn't matter.

37:55.910 --> 37:57.010
By that time,

37:58.720 --> 38:01.720
all the civil and military officials
will be present.

38:03.400 --> 38:05.600
Yu Wanyin's reputation as a seductress

38:06.480 --> 38:08.280
will spread forever.

38:10.630 --> 38:12.320
If Xiahou Dan shields her,

38:13.640 --> 38:15.620
then he's blinded by lust.

38:17.630 --> 38:19.290
He'd be an incompetent ruler.

38:21.110 --> 38:21.920
In this way,

38:22.550 --> 38:23.710
our military action

38:24.630 --> 38:25.400
will be...

38:28.000 --> 38:29.920
fully justified.
